o. info .o

ConvertXtoDVD is a 1 click solution to convert and burn your movie
files to a compatible DVD playable on your home DVD player
ConvertXtoDVD supports the most popular formats (including: DivX
Xvid, MOV, VOB, Mpeg, Mpeg4, AVI, WMV, DV) and subtitles
Choose fullscreen or widescreen (4:3 or 16:9) as well as NTSC or
PAL
Create your own menu, merge files, add custom chapters, remove
unwanted parts of the video such as commercials, rotate videos
change the brightness and contrast
Multiple audio and subtitle tracks are supported. Subtitles can be
converted as external subtitles or embedded into the video, and can
be tweaked by color, font, code page, positioning and more
Audio, video, and subtitle synchronization can be corrected with
an "offset" feature
Change output size and encoding quality and select the resize
filters you want to be used
Save the conversion to your hard drive, burn to ISO or DVD, single
or double layer disk
